         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year six of Imperator Caesar Titus Aelius Hadrianus Antoninus Augustus Pius. Work done on the dikes for the same 6th year, Payni 24 till 28, at the --- of the new sluice-gate, on behalf of Tebtunis, Kronion, son of Orseus the son of Orseus, his mother being Taarmiysis. (2nd h.) I, Chairias, have signed.</ab>
